getfield -1 doWhitelist
pcall 1 1 0
getglobal     print(p 
getfield -1  " whitelisted")
getglobal     table
getfield -1 insert(topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 whitelist, p)
getglobal end
getglobal function topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 unwhitelist
pcall 1 1 0
getglobal     for x, m in pairs(topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 whitelist) do
setfield -2 if m
getglobal             print(m 
getfield -1  " unwhitelisted")
getglobal             table
getfield -1 remove(topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 whitelist, x)
getglobal             if game
getfield -1 GetService
pushvalue -2
pcall 2 1 0
getfield -1 FindFirstChild then
pushvalue -2
pcall 2 1 0
getglobal                 topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 executeKick(game
getfield -1 GetService[p])
pushvalue -2
pcall 2 1 0
getglobal             end
getglobal         end
getglobal     end 
getglobal end
getglobal function topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 plrWhitelisted
pcall 1 1 0
getglobal     for x, m in pairs(topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 whitelist) do
setfield -2 if m
getglobal             return true
getglobal         end
getglobal     end 
getglobal     return false
getglobal end

getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 makePrivate
pcall 1 1 0 
getglobal topkek

pushboolean true
setfield -2 isPrivate
getglobal     for i, v in pairs(game
getfield -1 GetService
pushvalue -2
pcall 2 1 0

pushvalue -2
pcall 1 1 0)

getglobal if not topkek

setfield -2 plrWhitelisted(v) and v ~
getglobal             spawn
pcall 1 1 0 
getglobal                 topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 executeKick
pcall 1 1 0
getglobal             end)
getglobal         end
getglobal     end
getglobal end

pcall 2 1 0

getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 plrBanned or (topkek
pcall 1 1 0

getfield -1 isPrivate and not topkek
getfield -1 banmgr
getfield -1 plrWhitelisted) then
pcall 1 1 0
getglobal             print("Player " 
getfield -1  p
getfield -1 Name 
getfield -1  " is banned ! Kicking now
pcall 1 1 0
getfield -1 ")

getfield -1 banmgr

getglobal     end)
getglobal end
